{"tid":1493842,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"咪撚再話Eye4hk係鬼！","createTime":"2019-08-21T11:45:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T03:49:36.000Z","uid":192888,"like":476,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":84,"replies":[{"pid":"5ff9b42720e14e5e82b06231da885bdcf124a3a2","tid":1493842,"uid":192888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"Eye4hk<br />\n香港人係呢個運動上面係應該做帶領<br />\n香港人自己唔post樣 保護自己完全冇問題<br />\n相信大家都自己識風險評估<br />\n如果擔心個tag比人知ig係黃絲 就更加冇謂<br />\n日日大把人tag反送中 大把人post黃野<br />\n根本就冇問題<br />\n唔好再話有鬼冇鬼<br />\n用公仔又好用動物又好<br />\n最緊要係推到國際化！ 推到外國人響應關注<br />\n香港加油<br />\n同我推爆佢<br />\n8點就係！<br />\n<br />\n#Eye4HK<br />\n#EyeforHK<br />\n#NoPoliceBrutality<br />\n#FreeFromFear<br />\n#DemocracyForHK<br />\n<br />\n［#Eye4HK Campaign 一觸即發］已有名人強勢加盟！今晚八點正，約定大家喺各大社交媒體見，發動全球文宣！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1493145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1493145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"41da676a114b965c4af582d4f63ff590d05f94f8","tid":1493842,"uid":192888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:46:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6db66faa1bbc3c20f984cf5430d6c0f0771b355b","tid":1493842,"uid":192888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:46:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7e9d6a19e9846fe20fe1fb7fb46a91cd923aa530","tid":1493842,"uid":192888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da7465cfc5757f9e87f183f818dd72f4690a3883","tid":1493842,"uid":192888,"like":73,"dislike":3,"score":70,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkXs2bX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkXs2bX.png&h=8b5ccbea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a9871563006aeb9db77d9da5007b86acb0a500cf","tid":1493842,"uid":277084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T11:46:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b0e14619b24e3270ea173bfe2aa03d0aaf5fdc5e","t